text: Count Binface is a character created by Jon Harvey. He is a UK comedian. He was a candidate for Uxbridge and South Ruislip in the 2019 United Kingdom general election. He was called Lord Buckethead. He changed his name due to a copyright dispute with Todd Durham. Durham is the originator of the character. ==Related pages== *Count Binface *List of Uxbridge and South Ruislip 2019 election candidates *Lord Buckethead *Official Monster Raving Loony Party *Fandom of binface ==References== Category:British comedians Category:British politicians
